Title: ServiceNow: Added support for creation of cases
Class: feature
Compatible: compat
Component: notifications
Date: 1626868319
Edition: cee
Knowledge: undoc
Level: 1
Version: 2.1.0b1

Until now, only the creation of incidents was supported. With this werk, the
notification rule for Servicenow receives an option to use the management type
"Case" to create cases with the related notifications.

For now, problem and recovery notifications are supported. Acknowledgements and
downtime notifications are currently not supported.
